description: Demolition of existing buildings at Arklow Trading Estate, Arklow Road, SE14 and construction of mixed use development in buildings ranging from 5 to 9 storeys comprising 287 residential dwellings, 3,039sqm commercial floorspace (Classes A1, A2, A3, B1, D1 and D2 and ancillary uses), energy centre, disabled vehicle and cycle parking, landscaping, access and associated works.
